<span id="freeTextContainer15348322198626321516">A wonderful look at the hypocrisy of a &quot;religious&quot; preacher, Elmer Gantry. This book reminds me of Mark Twain&apos;s famous quote:<br/><br/>&quot;Religion was invented when the first con-man met the first fool.&quot;</span>
  <span id="freeText15348322198626321516" style="display:none">A wonderful look at the hypocrisy of a "religious" preacher, Elmer Gantry. This book reminds me of Mark Twain's famous quote:<br /><br />"Religion was invented when the first con-man met the first fool."</span>
